      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not like other things you \"bounce back\" from. you can lose a job or get a divorce and try to rebuild, but this is different. my name is toxic now. my entire identity was that role, that reputation. without it, there's literally nothing left of me. it feels like there's no path forward, just a void where a person used to be. it's like the world has already decided i don't exist anymore.",
